data.description:
Situated on the one of the largest lots in the neighborhood on a cul-de-sac with ample parking. Walk through brand-new modern impact front French doors into your dream home. You'll walk into an open concept living/dining area with split bedroom floor plan and vaulted ceilings in all rooms. The large master bedroom welcomes you with 2 closets and a completely remodeled master bathroom, including rain shower, modern free-standing bathtub and floating vanities. The guest bedrooms are both good sized, and include large closets with built ins. The guest bathroom was remodeled with a modern, glass top vanity and shower/tub combo. Step into the large kitchen with breakfast nook, remodeled with wood cabinets, pantry and high-end granite countertops. All stainless appliances, built-in wine cooler. Once you've taken in the interior, step outside to your own private oasis. Backyard includes a covered 27x8 patio, along with a private saltwater pool, all screened in so you can enjoy your evenings year-round, bug free! The pool offers an elevated sitting area and a tranquil waterfall. Mechanical features include color changing light, new filter and variable speed pump. Outside of the screened in pool sits a 12x12 gazebo with a large paver patio. Perfect for entertaining or just relaxing with a glass of wine. Gazebo has dedicated power and is pre-run for outdoor audio. The only thing this home needs is a new owner. 
All dimensions are approximate.
